OL,3,C'Disgruntlement and ill-feeling' among
OL,4,CNI Water staff on strike over pay
OL,6,FSome workers at NI Water have begun
OL,7,Findustrial action due to a dispute
OL,8,Fover pay arrangements.
OL,10,FThe one-day strike is by non-frontline
OL,11,Fmembers of the Nipsa union.
OL,13,FWork-to-rule action is expected to
OL,14,Fstart on January 1.
OL,16,FSpeaking during the strike in Belfast,
OL,17,FNipsa general secretary Carmel Gates
OL,18,Fsaid: "If a solution is not found we
OL,19,Ffear there will be more action and
OL,20,Fdisruption."
