OL,6,F"Given that the weather is expected to
OL,7,Fturn for the worse, this is not a time
OL,8,Fwhen we want water affected.
OL,10,F"We are asking for management to be
OL,11,Freasonable, come to the table and
OL,12,Fresolve the issues.
OL,14,F"Let these workers get off the picket
OL,15,Fline," Ms Gates said.
OL,17,FMeanwhile in Londonderry, union
OL,18,Fcommittee member Paddy Harkin said
OL,19,Fthere is "a lot of disgruntlement and
OL,20,Fill-feeling" amongst members.
