OL,3,C'Disgruntlement and ill-feeling' among
OL,4,CNI Water staff on strike over pay
OL,6,FNI Water's Director of People &
OL,7,FLearning, Rose Kelly said: "Ministers
OL,8,FKimmins and O'Dowd have authorised pay
OL,9,Fawards in line with the wider public
OL,10,Fsector for 2024/2025 and 2025/2026
OL,11,Fthat have been accepted by our
OL,12,Ffrontline unions Unite and GMB.
OL,14,F"This dispute however centres on a
OL,15,Ftechnical issue around how NI Water
OL,16,Fand Nipsa negotiate pay for a section
OL,17,Fof our workforce, and the company has
OL,18,Fproposed an appropriate route for
OL,19,FNipsa to secure that determination.
