OL,4,CNI Water staff on strike over pay
OL,6,F"NI Water has made repeated efforts
OL,7,Fthroughout 2025 to engage with Nipsa,
OL,8,Fincluding taking part in mediation
OL,9,Fearlier this month, and we remain open
OL,10,Fto continued discussion with the
OL,11,Funion," she added.
OL,13,F"NI Water has a pay offer ready and
OL,14,Fhas encouraged Nipsa to submit a pay
OL,15,Fclaim for all non-frontline employees
OL,16,Fto enable pay negotiations to commence
OL,17,Fwithout delay.
